res = ''
for _ in range(int(input())):
    (n, m) = map(int, input().split())
    res += ('NO\n', 'YES\n')[n % m == 0]
print(res)

t = int(input())
for i in range(t):
    a = list(map(int, input().split(' ')))
    print(('NO', 'YES')[a[0] % a[1] == 0 or a[1] % a[0] == 0])

m = int(input())

for i in l:
    print(i)
